{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Mijn portfolio's door de jaren heen</h1>\n<p>Hoewel ik nog niet zo lang geleden aan mijn opleiding informatica begon zijn mijn portfolio websites wel flink wat veranderd, qua design en qua intenties die ik met website wou bereiken. Hier laat ik in chronologische volgorde zien hoe mijn portfolio zich in de loop van mijn studie heeft ontwikkeld. Je kunt ook de verschillende designs terug zien op <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180701000000*/stevenkoerts.nl\">The Way-Back-Machine</a> van <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/\">web.archive.org</a>. Een website die van heel veel websites een screenshot heeft van verschillende jaren, leuk voor als je bijvoorbeeld wilt weten hoe YouTube eruit zag op 23 april 2005. </p>\n<h3>Mijn portfolio in 2016</h3>\n<p>Uitsluitend primaire kleuren, niet schaalbaar, niet responsive. Het bevat overigens de minimale informatie die een werkgever nodig heeft en wat nodige extra's. </p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ff50b4d12365cb14ee1981993e831623/d5788/portfolio-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 54%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"portfolio 1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ff50b4d12365cb14ee1981993e831623/dbb61/portfolio-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ff50b4d12365cb14ee1981993e831623/19bd1/portfolio-1.png 163w,\n/static/ff50b4d12365cb14ee1981993e831623/d3bcb/portfolio-1.png 325w,\n/static/ff50b4d12365cb14ee1981993e831623/dbb61/portfolio-1.png 650w,\n/static/ff50b4d12365cb14ee1981993e831623/6b691/portfolio-1.png 975w,\n/static/ff50b4d12365cb14ee1981993e831623/91670/portfolio-1.png 1300w,\n/static/ff50b4d12365cb14ee1981993e831623/d5788/portfolio-1.png 1900w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/25d9ec285a9fc2a9e197b7c764344d29/a6bc7/portfolio-1-videos-contact.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 54.19525065963061%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"portfolio videos\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/25d9ec285a9fc2a9e197b7c764344d29/dbb61/portfolio-1-videos-contact.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/25d9ec285a9fc2a9e197b7c764344d29/19bd1/portfolio-1-videos-contact.png 163w,\n/static/25d9ec285a9fc2a9e197b7c764344d29/d3bcb/portfolio-1-videos-contact.png 325w,\n/static/25d9ec285a9fc2a9e197b7c764344d29/dbb61/portfolio-1-videos-contact.png 650w,\n/static/25d9ec285a9fc2a9e197b7c764344d29/6b691/portfolio-1-videos-contact.png 975w,\n/static/25d9ec285a9fc2a9e197b7c764344d29/91670/portfolio-1-videos-contact.png 1300w,\n/static/25d9ec285a9fc2a9e197b7c764344d29/a6bc7/portfolio-1-videos-contact.png 1895w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>En een mooie error pagina kan ook niet ontbreken.\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/180eda10d94e11912f6ef27b30bdffc6/c381c/portfolio-1-error.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 58.59117840684661%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"error page\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/180eda10d94e11912f6ef27b30bdffc6/dbb61/portfolio-1-error.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/180eda10d94e11912f6ef27b30bdffc6/19bd1/portfolio-1-error.png 163w,\n/static/180eda10d94e11912f6ef27b30bdffc6/d3bcb/portfolio-1-error.png 325w,\n/static/180eda10d94e11912f6ef27b30bdffc6/dbb61/portfolio-1-error.png 650w,\n/static/180eda10d94e11912f6ef27b30bdffc6/6b691/portfolio-1-error.png 975w,\n/static/180eda10d94e11912f6ef27b30bdffc6/91670/portfolio-1-error.png 1300w,\n/static/180eda10d94e11912f6ef27b30bdffc6/c381c/portfolio-1-error.png 1519w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3>In 2017 heb ik al wat meer geleerd over webdevelopment</h3>\n<p>Hoewel is mijn website wel even in onderhoud geweest.\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/78a7674f47b436eb4c2a6ebc6c57924e/7bc83/portfolio-onderhoudt.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 47.371303395399785%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"onderhoud website\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/78a7674f47b436eb4c2a6ebc6c57924e/dbb61/portfolio-onderhoudt.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/78a7674f47b436eb4c2a6ebc6c57924e/19bd1/portfolio-onderhoudt.png 163w,\n/static/78a7674f47b436eb4c2a6ebc6c57924e/d3bcb/portfolio-onderhoudt.png 325w,\n/static/78a7674f47b436eb4c2a6ebc6c57924e/dbb61/portfolio-onderhoudt.png 650w,\n/static/78a7674f47b436eb4c2a6ebc6c57924e/6b691/portfolio-onderhoudt.png 975w,\n/static/78a7674f47b436eb4c2a6ebc6c57924e/91670/portfolio-onderhoudt.png 1300w,\n/static/78a7674f47b436eb4c2a6ebc6c57924e/7bc83/portfolio-onderhoudt.png 1826w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Ik besloot om een website te bouwen met Python en Django, de hosting werd wel wat duurder voor Python website. Dus heb ik Django gebruikt als een statische website builder.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/890ef0694b7fe8d3321422537f4ebaa7/a6bc7/python-website.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 47.17678100263852%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"python django website\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/890ef0694b7fe8d3321422537f4ebaa7/dbb61/python-website.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/890ef0694b7fe8d3321422537f4ebaa7/19bd1/python-website.png 163w,\n/static/890ef0694b7fe8d3321422537f4ebaa7/d3bcb/python-website.png 325w,\n/static/890ef0694b7fe8d3321422537f4ebaa7/dbb61/python-website.png 650w,\n/static/890ef0694b7fe8d3321422537f4ebaa7/6b691/python-website.png 975w,\n/static/890ef0694b7fe8d3321422537f4ebaa7/91670/python-website.png 1300w,\n/static/890ef0694b7fe8d3321422537f4ebaa7/a6bc7/python-website.png 1895w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Ik had in iedergeval een dynamische manier om projecten toe te voegen, vandaar die <strong>Next-</strong>button.\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dc6761c6dfa5ec0721eff0fbee886739/6fc51/python-project.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 90.37871033776868%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Python django projects\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dc6761c6dfa5ec0721eff0fbee886739/dbb61/python-project.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dc6761c6dfa5ec0721eff0fbee886739/19bd1/python-project.png 163w,\n/static/dc6761c6dfa5ec0721eff0fbee886739/d3bcb/python-project.png 325w,\n/static/dc6761c6dfa5ec0721eff0fbee886739/dbb61/python-project.png 650w,\n/static/dc6761c6dfa5ec0721eff0fbee886739/6b691/python-project.png 975w,\n/static/dc6761c6dfa5ec0721eff0fbee886739/6fc51/python-project.png 977w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Op dit moment had ik ook Bootstrap ontdenkt.\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/440873f537c97f1db492879cc4e9480b/02da8/portfolio-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 46.008403361344534%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"bootstrap 4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/440873f537c97f1db492879cc4e9480b/dbb61/portfolio-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/440873f537c97f1db492879cc4e9480b/19bd1/portfolio-4.png 163w,\n/static/440873f537c97f1db492879cc4e9480b/d3bcb/portfolio-4.png 325w,\n/static/440873f537c97f1db492879cc4e9480b/dbb61/portfolio-4.png 650w,\n/static/440873f537c97f1db492879cc4e9480b/6b691/portfolio-4.png 975w,\n/static/440873f537c97f1db492879cc4e9480b/91670/portfolio-4.png 1300w,\n/static/440873f537c97f1db492879cc4e9480b/02da8/portfolio-4.png 1904w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3>In 2018 ging ik volledig over op een statische website</h3>\n<p>Docusaurus is ook geschikt als portfolio, niet alleen voor Facebooks open source documentatie. </p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2f3723e53be3fe949f5a72aa291bda82/a987b/portfolio-docusaurus.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"docusaurus website\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2f3723e53be3fe949f5a72aa291bda82/dbb61/portfolio-docusaurus.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2f3723e53be3fe949f5a72aa291bda82/19bd1/portfolio-docusaurus.png 163w,\n/static/2f3723e53be3fe949f5a72aa291bda82/d3bcb/portfolio-docusaurus.png 325w,\n/static/2f3723e53be3fe949f5a72aa291bda82/dbb61/portfolio-docusaurus.png 650w,\n/static/2f3723e53be3fe949f5a72aa291bda82/6b691/portfolio-docusaurus.png 975w,\n/static/2f3723e53be3fe949f5a72aa291bda82/91670/portfolio-docusaurus.png 1300w,\n/static/2f3723e53be3fe949f5a72aa291bda82/a987b/portfolio-docusaurus.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/795381cc19aa67eab3f77a1d5cdcfefc/a987b/portfolio-docusaurus-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"docusaurus website\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/795381cc19aa67eab3f77a1d5cdcfefc/dbb61/portfolio-docusaurus-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/795381cc19aa67eab3f77a1d5cdcfefc/19bd1/portfolio-docusaurus-2.png 163w,\n/static/795381cc19aa67eab3f77a1d5cdcfefc/d3bcb/portfolio-docusaurus-2.png 325w,\n/static/795381cc19aa67eab3f77a1d5cdcfefc/dbb61/portfolio-docusaurus-2.png 650w,\n/static/795381cc19aa67eab3f77a1d5cdcfefc/6b691/portfolio-docusaurus-2.png 975w,\n/static/795381cc19aa67eab3f77a1d5cdcfefc/91670/portfolio-docusaurus-2.png 1300w,\n/static/795381cc19aa67eab3f77a1d5cdcfefc/a987b/portfolio-docusaurus-2.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3>Nu Anno 2019</h3>\n<p>Bleek een volledige React based static site generator de ideale oplossing, ik ben benieuwd hoe mijn website zich verder ontwikkeld. </p>\n<iframe min-height=\"250px\" src=\"http://stevenkoerts.nl\"></iframe>\n<p><em>#MadeWithGatsby</em></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mijn portfolio's door de jaren heen","date":"2019-05-07","category":"blog"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/Mijn-portfolios-door-de-jaren-heen/"}}